<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śubhamastu <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> śālivā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>hanaśakavaruśa 1471
<lb n="3"/>neya sau(ṁ)myasaṁ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vatsarada puśya śu 9 lu
<lb n="5"/>śrīmanmahārājā
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="6" break="no"/>dhirāja rājaparamēśvara
<lb n="7"/>śrīvīrāpratāpa śrī
<lb n="8" break="no"/>vīraśadāsivadēvamahā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>rāyaru makarasaṁkrāṁ
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ti puṇyakāladalu
<lb n="11"/>jaṁbukēśvarada beṭa 
</p>

<!--<h4>Third Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="12" break="no"/>da hanuvaṁtadēvara neyi
<lb n="13" break="no"/>vēdyake Anaṁtaśayana
<lb n="14" break="no"/>dēvara Amrutapaḍige saluva
<lb n="15"/>svāstiyoḷage nāu kaṭṭaḷeya
<lb n="16"/>māḍi <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> dina 1 kke Akki
</p>

<!--<h4>Fourth Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="17"/>pa 4 Ī nālkupaḍi Akki
<lb n="18" break="no"/>yanu Ācaṁdrārkastāyi
<lb n="19" break="no"/>yāgi naḍavahāge kaṭṭu
<lb n="20"/>māḍi silāśāsanava hā
<lb n="21" break="no"/>kisi koṭeU <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied>
</p>

